  "description": "Cookie Clicker datapack: click to earn cookies, buy upgrades, unlock automation, and build a steadily growing resource empire. [1.21.9 - 26.1.x]",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <h1>Cookie Clicker</h1>\n  <br/>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://nat688.github.io/AllPlugs-datapacks/cookie-clicker.html\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Wiki-Cookie%20Clicker_(soon)-gold?logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,\" alt=\"Wiki Link\">\n    </a>\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Beta-1.0.0snapshot_8-darkorange\" alt=\"Release\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Minecraft-1.21.9%2026.1.x-blue?logo=data:image/png;base64,&logoWidth=50\" alt=\"Minecraft\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/License-CC_BY_4.0-blueviolet\" alt=\"License CC BY 4.0\">\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/Tq83Zuhduv\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1358706268012810350?color=5865F2&label=Discord&logo=discord&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\">\n    </a>\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/qdD2dPbY?logo=modrinth&label=Modrinth\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<h2>✨ Features</h2> \n<h3>🔥 Main description</h3> \n<blockquote> \n  This feature introduces a cookie-based progression system inspired by incremental games.<br/> \n  Players receive a special cookie item in their inventory that can be right-clicked to generate resources over time.<br/>\n  Combined with a custom shop, this creates a loop where players actively and passively increase their production — turning simple actions into a growing resource empire. \n</blockquote> \n<h3>🍪 Core mechanic</h3> \n<blockquote> \n  Players start with a unique cookie item that acts as the main interaction tool.<br/> \n  Right-clicking the cookie generates currency or resources, forming the foundation of the progression system.<br/>\n  Over time, this manual interaction can be enhanced, optimized, or partially automated through upgrades. \n</blockquote> \n<h3>🛒 Shop system</h3> \n<blockquote> \n  A dedicated shop allows players to spend their generated resources on upgrades.<br/> \n  These upgrades can improve click power, unlock passive generation, or boost overall efficiency.<br/> \n  The shop creates a clear progression path, encouraging players to strategically invest and continuously scale their production. \n</blockquote> \n<h3>⚙️ Use and benefits</h3> \n<blockquote> \n  This system offers an alternative progression style focused on growth and optimization rather than exploration alone.<br/>\n  It provides a satisfying feedback loop: click → earn → upgrade → earn faster.<br/>\n  Players gain more control over their progression speed while enjoying a steady sense of advancement. \n</blockquote> \n<h3>🧩 Gameplay integration</h3> \n<blockquote> \n  Designed to fit seamlessly into Minecraft, this feature uses simple interactions (inventory item + right-click) and optional interfaces for the shop.<br/> \n  It can coexist with survival gameplay while adding a new layer of strategy centered around resource management and scaling systems. \n</blockquote>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2>💬 Commands</h2>\n<blockquote>\n  <code>/trigger _cookie_clicker_start</code> - gives you the cookie to click<br/><br/>\n  <code>/trigger _cookie_clicker_shop</code> - open the shop with all the buildings to buy<br/><br/>\n  <code>/trigger _cookie_clicker_stats</code> - tells you how many buildings you own<br/><br/>\n  <code>/trigger _cookie_clicker_reset</code> - resets your progress<br/><br/>\n  <code>/trigger cookie_clicker_buy_<building></code> - buy the buildings directly without the shop<br/>\n</blockquote>\n\n<br/>\n\n<h2>📥 Installation</h2>\n<h3>📁 Datapack</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Drop the <code>.zip</code> file into your world's <code>datapacks</code> folder.<br/>\n  Reload the world or use <code>/reload</code>.<br/>\n  Enjoy your enchanted adventure!\n</blockquote>\n\n<h3>⚙️ Mod</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  Drop the <code>.jar</code> file into the <code>mods</code> folder of your instance.<br/>\n  <code>Restart</code> your game.<br/>\n  Have fun!\n</blockquote>",
